tool_description: Train your own machine learning project Stop wasting time scrolling through a list of videos. Use our Youtube classification API to get the information you need in the most efficient way possible. With our API and your favorite programming language, you can classify videos into like count, comment count, and rating count so that you can find what you're looking for in no time.

import requests

url = "https://youtube-classification-api.p.rapidapi.com/1/2/3/4/5/6/7"

            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "youtube-classification-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
